{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"becfb06e98","title":"对吴晗再次要求入党的来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de2f761cac","index":0,"year":1952,"month":7,"day":22,"articleId":"becfb06e98"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"d30aabffe8","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指吴哈1952年7月21日为再次要求加入中国共产党给毛泽东的信。他在信中提到1949年1月3日曾向毛泽东提出入党请求，同年1月14日毛泽东给他回信说：“我们同意你的要求。惟实行时机尚值得研究，详请思来同志面告。1952年7月以后，吴晗又多次提出入党要求。1957年3月，吴哈被中共中央正式批准加入中国共产党。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e9091f8dfd","type":"title","text":"对吴晗叫再次要求人党的来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98"},{"id":"d30aabffe8","type":"paragraph","text":"我意还是暂不入党为宜。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98"},{"id":"02c16bab5e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98"},{"id":"3c7b1f6f46","type":"paragraph","text":"七月廿二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98"},{"id":"1858c66401","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]吴晗，当时任北京市人民政府副市长、中国民主同盟北京市支部委员会主任委员。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98"}],"page":{"id":"41906f3951","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"becfb06e98","start":175,"end":175}}}},"__N_SSG":true}